{"tid":759254,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟否認與美國 就開放農產品市場磋商","createTime":"2018-07-28T12:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T12:55:26.000Z","uid":147097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51927423cdc3da6a52ec3866c6b85e9117ba2ec0","tid":759254,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）日前宣稱已為美國農民打開歐洲市場，惟歐盟斷言否認，指除歐美貿易協議提到的內容外，其餘農產品均不在貿易談判範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟委員會主席容克（Jean-Claude Juncker）周三與特朗普會面後達成貿易協議，當中一項涉及農產品，就是歐盟將增加購入美國大豆。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普一日後在艾奧瓦州向民眾表示，政府剛為農民打開歐洲市場，形容農民終於可進入龐大的市場。<br />\n<br />\n惟歐盟委員會發言人安德烈耶娃（Mina Andreeva）周五在比利時布魯塞爾向記者表示，農產品不在歐美貿易談判範圍之內，「除協議中明顯列出的內容外，我們不會就農產品作談判。」<br />\n<br />\n容克周五亦稱，歐美周三的談判幾乎拉倒，主因美方堅持要將整個農產品領域納入討論，但歐盟方面反對。<br />\n<br />\n美國作為農業大國，一直希望外國增加購入該國的農產品，有關議題卻成為美國與多國遲遲無法達成貿易協議的障礙，包括歐盟及日本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5aff822fb95b7c673c6407c4f51b9a3c9be580","tid":759254,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"EU唔會要GM豆。"},{"pid":"a9f41d1b25bf9cbcb8dd28c957b2033acb5579e5","tid":759254,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f5aff822fb95b7c673c6407c4f51b9a3c9be580","tid":759254,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"EU唔會要GM豆。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14926686630cacf72a8550aa2f303b22140622a","tid":759254,"uid":64347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9f41d1b25bf9cbcb8dd28c957b2033acb5579e5","tid":759254,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f5aff822fb95b7c673c6407c4f51b9a3c9be580","tid":759254,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"EU唔會要GM豆。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"有冇食過百福豆腐花, 都係用GM豆造<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有數不盡既食品係用GM豆油, 畜養業都係用GM豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab5ebb154c7090c74881733c31165132e3a23c3","tid":759254,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14926686630cacf72a8550aa2f303b22140622a","tid":759254,"uid":64347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9f41d1b25bf9cbcb8dd28c957b2033acb5579e5","tid":759254,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f5aff822fb95b7c673c6407c4f51b9a3c9be580","tid":759254,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"EU唔會要GM豆。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"有冇食過百福豆腐花, 都係用GM豆造<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有數不盡既食品係用GM豆油, 畜養業都係用GM豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}